Package: framerd-imagetools
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd (= ${binary:Version}), libexif12, libmagickwand5, libqrencode3
Description: Image tools for FramerD
  Bindings to various image libraries modules for FramerD,
  including ImageMagick, QRCode generation, and EXIF extraction.

